{"tid":32180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭5漢灌醉輪姦丟路邊 兩女童當場精神失常 !!!!","createTime":"2016-12-10T05:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T00:53:28.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ea0d0fdf56173846b523ce4d08e36b69176268","tid":32180,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:08:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161210/56023938\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161210%2F56023938&d=Q1Lc9FxxPPjRZGjVx3LN1ksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=4a591934\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161210%2F56023938&h=edd0238f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161210/56023938</a><br />\n<br />\n泰國芭堤雅周二發生一宗輪姦案轟動全國，兩名女童慘遭5名男子灌醉輪姦，被發現時精神失常。警方周三拘捕4名疑犯，仍有一人在逃。<br />\n<br />\n警方周二晚接報指兩名女童遭人強姦後被丟在海灘附近的路上，警察到場時發現13歲的小碧及14歲的小艾爛醉如泥、全身抽搐和精神渙散，身心遭受巨大創傷，其中一人更出現癲狂症狀及階段性痙攣，警方馬上安排她們入院治理。<br />\n<br />\n案中一名疑犯供稱，事發時看見小碧及小艾在海邊閒逛，遇到數名男子搭訕並邀請她們一起飲酒，數名男子趁她們神志不清時將她們帶到附近一處平房淫辱，完事後就將她們丟在路邊。<br />\n<br />\n有村民向警方表示疑犯曾一度回來，丟下兩名女童的手袋後開電單車離去。<br />\n<br />\n警方周三拘捕4名年齡介乎16至22歲的疑犯，並帶其中3人到現場重組案情。疑犯強調兩名女童是自願與他們發生性關係，但警方指由於她們都未成年，故無論她們是否自願都構成違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n警方初步以輪姦未滿15歲少女罪名起訴5名男子，又提醒女性要注意安全，盡量避免晚上獨自外出。<br />\n<br />\n泰國《世界日報》/泰國網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161209/large/1481269979_a7d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161209%2Flarge%2F1481269979_a7d4.jpg&h=b4445c38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161209/large/1481269980_b536.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161209%2Flarge%2F1481269980_b536.png&h=d1d977c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161209/large/1481269982_727e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161209%2Flarge%2F1481269982_727e.png&h=dcf50dbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161209/large/1481269986_341d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161209%2Flarge%2F1481269986_341d.jpg&h=63a615e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161210/large/1481330929_54d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161210%2Flarge%2F1481330929_54d6.jpg&h=9de461e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51d79a3d24cf3e6452c0c4860eb068bddb4f8b2c","tid":32180,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:11:26.000Z","msg":"人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f91383e4454c7420c5880675f61608889cd4b4","tid":32180,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"係咪男童嚟㗎？<br />\n<br />\n不過個幾條友正垃圾<br />\n變性之後送佢地去印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab953a099c4c2590590f3c13c2f15ac8f06d34da","tid":32180,"uid":18421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3848cf9791a0d8111509d331a45294b0610118","tid":32180,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:16:53.000Z","msg":"13歲少女竟然有這麼大的奶奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78fe528e7738e4d4b3f4b2c16312feb00a64ad54","tid":32180,"uid":24739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"應該要有閹刑<img src=